Invocation Name: stock hub
des:
Ask for stock prices and upcoming earnings,

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Stocks Hub" or "Alexa, open Stocks Hub" to get latest stock prices and earnings dates ".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
